snippet.title: The Next Mass Effect - Official Teaser Trailer
snippet.description: Get a sneak peek at the next chapter of the Mass Effect universe. A veteran team at BioWare is in the early stages of what is on the horizon for the Mass Effect franchise, and we are excited to show you where we’ll be heading next!
